                        fine, regular, Edessene hand of the <date calendar="Gregorian" notBefore="0400" notAfter="0500">vth</date> or <date calendar="Gregorian" notBefore="0500" notAfter="0600">vith
                          cent</date>., with the exception of foll. 44 and 45, which are
                        comparatively modern and palimpsest (see below).</p>
